{"tid":2281510,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麵咪媽 能否繼續騙金錢","createTime":"2020-11-11T08:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T13:28:41.000Z","uid":60658,"like":55,"dislike":246,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"fe6172f80c6d84169ffcf142d8041f87e41d728d","tid":2281510,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"&lt;&lt;金錢師&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n作詞：N_Bendtner, H_Lozano<br />\n作曲：夢不捨遺<br />\n編曲：政命靴里拉<br />\n監製：佩雷斯主任<br />\n<br />\n麵咪媽 能否繼續騙金錢<br />\n佢假裝演有 腦癌來呃鳩你<br />\n就算有錢炒股無錢醫腦癌 財經台傻仔會可憐<br />\n<br />\n麵咪媽 做乜要上嚟乞錢<br />\n還是佢玩牛熊 或是佢炒燶股 或是呃錢<br />\n螞蟻集團上市徒然又試　始終得不到妳在意<br />\n<br />\n連登真的很多的白痴<br />\n黃絲信十足　每日也都會課金<br />\n太心痛是我的一手包辦令妳心變酸 彌補如何還是太遲"},{"pid":"be031e9c9b195e87de100dbdc9c232dd8359778d","tid":2281510,"uid":124891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19060625320ccdcf1b1edded90c573c1e9c61319","tid":2281510,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa1968c896f4f440a0e2b7442397e07ac9760a0","tid":2281510,"uid":38189,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19060625320ccdcf1b1edded90c573c1e9c61319","tid":2281510,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"啱音嘅係我填<br />\n更啱音嘅係樓主填"},{"pid":"3db189ad2ead6741863fdc621e5bf21d5b54a5d1","tid":2281510,"uid":60658,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fa1968c896f4f440a0e2b7442397e07ac9760a0","tid":2281510,"uid":38189,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19060625320ccdcf1b1edded90c573c1